
<p class="p-3 m-3 border border-primary bg-light">
    This website includes information about the first 
    809 Pokemon in the Pokedex. You can search for 
    them by their name, pokedex number, type, category,
    and capture rate. You will be able to indicate which
    pokemons you have, which you've seen, and your favorites.
    You must signup or login to see the pokemon and to add
    them to those lists.
</p>
    <% if (true || loggedIn) {%>  
        <form method="post" action="/pokemon/byName">
            Show Pokemon by Name: 
              <input type="text" name="name" 
                     placeholder="e.g. Squirtle">
            <input type="submit">
        </form>
        <br>
        <form method="post" action="/pokemon/byPokedexNum">
            Show Pokemon by Pokedex Number: 
            <input type="number" name="pokedexNum" 
                   placeholder="e.g. 13">
            <input type="submit">
        </form>
        <br>
        <form method="post" action="/pokemon/byType">
            Show Pokemon by Type: 
            <input type="text" name="type" 
                   placeholder="e.g. Poison">
            <input type="submit">
        </form>
        <br>
        <form method="post" action="/pokemon/byCategory">
            Show Pokemon by Category: 
            <input type="text" name="category" 
                   placeholder="e.g. Gas">
            <input type="submit">
        </form>
        <br>
        <form method="post" action="/pokemon/byCaptureRate">
            Show Pokemon by Minimum Capture Rate: 
            <input type="number" name="captureRate" 
                   placeholder="e.g. 50">
            <input type="submit">
        </form>
        <br>
        <a href="/pokemon/myStats">Show my Stats</a>
    <% } %>


